Rodrigo was born in Sagunto (Valencia), and completely lost his sight at the age of three after contracting diphtheria.

Rodrigo was born in Sagunto (Valencia), and completely lost his sight at the age of three after contracting diphtheria.

He is best known for composing the Concierto de Aranjuez, a cornerstone of the classical guitar repertoire.
